translations.Cannot reach the signd.it server. Please: Cannot reach the signd.it server. Please try again later.

translations.Login failed. Please check your credenti: Login failed. Please check your credentials.
translations.No API key configured. Please enter your: No API key configured. Please enter your API key, log in, or register a new account.

translations.Not enough storage space or insufficient: Not enough storage space or insufficient permissions. Please free up space and try again.
translations.Original folder no longer exists. Signed: Original folder no longer exists. Signed PDF was saved to your home folder.
The API key is linked to a single signd.it account. All signing processes run through this account, are billed to it, and are visible to all users regardless of who initiated them.
